  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to compare four different lung recruitment techniques (described in
      literature) to Computed tomography scan analysis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The investigators aim to compare four different lung recruitment techniques (described in
      literature) to Computed tomography scan analysis:

        -  stress index technique

        -  peep test

        -  recruitment technique used in the EXPRESS study

        -  recruitment technique used in the LOV study
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
